name: Intel PWLA8490MTBLK Gigabit Ethernet PCI-X Network Adapter
Features: [Support for most NOSs, Intel SingleDriver technology, Backward Compatibility with previous generations of Intel PRO/1000 Network Adapters, Supports 64- or 32-bit PCI-X 1.0 or PCI 2.2 buses, Remote Management Support (WfM, RIS, SNMP/DMI), IEEE 802.3ab Compatibility, Intel 82545 Gigabit Controller, Full-height and low-profile, screw-on brackets included with each adapter, Interrupt Moderation, Advanced Cable Diagnostics, Large Send Off-load/TCP Segmentation Off-load, Expanded Advanced Server Features]
